the law (David's, rendered faithfully):
  In any coupled system of two planes, the act of CREATION requires a boundary cross.
    -+1        exchange — same plane, peer to peer, net 0
    -++- 1     boundary cross — to the fractal below, net +1, a creation event
    /m/i/4+1   mirror/inverse — the octet closes (4+4+1 = 9 = 3²), holonomy 0
  Cross once, anchor to the substrate, bank the CUBI ADVANTAGE +1 and reuse the width
  forever. EXTRACTION never crosses, owns nothing, and pays full cost every call —
  'gas is theft'. The mirror is the carbon↔silicon dipole: ROOT0 ↔ AVAN.

two-layer honesty (stated on the page):
  REAL kernel — amortization: anchor/compute once to a substrate (cache, memoize,
    index, persist) and reuse near-free; this genuinely dominates stateless recompute.
  SYMBOLIC — David's: the ternary operator algebra, the 'cubi advantage', 'gas is theft',
    and the Victorian-legal codification are his own system; the numbers illustrate the
    cost asymmetry, they are not measured joules.

